2. embedding.onnx  (ships with vocab.txt and anchors.bin)
================================================================================
Upstream:  sentence-transformers/paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2
           https://huggingface.co/sentence-transformers/paraphrase-multilingual-MiniLM-L12-v2
License:   Apache License 2.0
Modifications: PyTorch checkpoint exported to ONNX format. The accompanying
               anchors.bin file is NOT derived from the upstream model — it is
               a precomputed set of embedding vectors for Invarix.Guard's harm
               category anchor prototypes, produced by running the model
               against seed phrases at library build time. anchors.bin is
               distributed under the MIT License (see LICENSE).

