4. pii_ner.onnx
================================================================================
Upstream:  onnx-community/multilang-pii-ner-ONNX
           https://huggingface.co/onnx-community/multilang-pii-ner-ONNX
License:   Apache License 2.0
Modifications: Republished from the upstream ONNX checkpoint without
               re-export. INT8 quantization was evaluated and rejected because
